> = 001 & ~(100)
> = 001 & 011
> = 001
> therefore the if condition is true
> therefore the function returns NULL from line 378.
> 
> Now in sys_timer_create() at line number 462
> Process = NULL
> 
> Now at line 489
> if (!process) becomes TRUE
> and function returns with EINVAL
> 
